title: Meeting The Families: Part 5
body:
*CRASH!*

*the two red pandas crash through the house, as Retsuko tumbles into the kitchen, plates dropping, and breaking on her*

Retsuko: AGH! STILL ALIVE, ASSHOLE!

Ryota: AS IF THAT WAS THE POINT. *lunges at her, to which she dodges* ALL THESE YEARS, YOU STILL HAVE YET TO LEARN A THING I TAUGHT YOU.

Retsuko: LIKE THERE WAS ANYTHING TO BE TAUGHT!

*as they continue to fight, the other family members sneak through the wreckage*

Haida: This is not good. We need a way to calm them, somehow!

Hiroko: I could hold them up!

Rie: That will only do so much, though. The rage itself needs to be neutralized.

Riko: ….where’s Ikari?

Haida: ….oh NO. *runs in* Ikari! IKARI!

Ikari: *in another room* ….dada?

Haida: *hearing the voice, and runs further into the house*

Hisoka: Come on! *the rest follow suit*

Ryuu: Aagh, why the hell am I even helping you guys?! I don’t even care what happens to her! Or the kid!

Rie: Because you still live in the same house as me, and I am willing to ground you for a long time.

Ryuu: ……point taken. *looks around* …Iraki?

Riko: IKARI!

Ryuu: Right, thanks! Ikari! *looks to the side of himself, and….* Found him!

*he’s in the dining room, right in the middle, all by himself*

Ikari: ….bah-bah! :D

Ryuu: Urgh, there you ar-*to the side, he sees Ryota, demonically looking at the infant, almost as if for blood* ……dad, no. Don’t.

Ryota: SHUT IT! NOW SHE WILL KNOW TRUE LOSS!

*the two charge towards the baby, but at the last second, Retsuko and Haida lunged in from an angle, at Ryota, leaving Ryuu to grab Ikari*

Haida: Take him to safety! GO!

Ryuu: Got it! *runs off*

Ryota: HEH. GOT EVERYONE AGAINST ME NOW?

Retsuko: JUST ENOUGH TO KEEP YOU AWAY!

Haida: Can you two just calm down? Let’s not make this any wors-

Retsuko: AFTER THIS LONG?! IT DESERVES TO BE WORSE!

Ryota: FOR ONCE, WE SEEM TO AGREE. *lunges at Retsuko, grabs ahold of her, and THROWS her through the wall, outside, and runs after her, as she crashes into the temple*

Retsuko: *falls onto the floor, coughing out some blood* ACK! YOU DID THIS! ANY GOOD FATHER WOULD HAVE NEVER DONE THIS TO THEIR CHILD!

Ryota: *storms in* SO I’M NOT A GOOD FATHER NOW?! WITH A BRAT LIKE YOU, HOW COULD I BE?! IT’S BEEN A LONG TIME COMING, RETSUKO, SO MANY YEARS OF PENT UP ANGER….BUT NOW, IN THE RESTING PLACE OF YOUR DEAR GRANDMOTHER, WE SHALL SETTLE THIS ONCE AND FOR ALL!

Retsuko: BRING I-*Ryota grabs her by the throat!* *ACK!*

Ryota: *SLAMS her on the wall with the urn, choking her* YOU LIKE THAT, HUH?!

Retsuko: *AGH!* P-PLEASE….STOP…..DAAAAD..!

Haida: *running in* Stop it! Ryota! THAT’S RETSUKO!

Ryota: I DON’T CARE! SHE WILL PAY! SHE…SHE WILL…..*he slowly lets her go, as she becomes unconscious….and his rage devolves….into utter horror* ……..R-Retsuk-*SMASH!* ……*falls to the ground, unconscious, in a pile of shattered urn pieces, and ashes*

Haida: *runs up to the two* No, no! NO! HELP HEEEEELLLP! HEEEEEEEELLLLLLLLP!!!!!!!!!

Like I stated previously, I am not the world’s best author of fight scenes. Which is amusing to me, as I love them. But yeah, overall, this was a pain to write. All the silly fight cliche lines I had to think up, all the intensity….yeah, it was not super fun. But hey! I got it done! Almost wrapped up with this arc, got about….a chapter or two left. Which then, I can FINALLY show my announcement. Until then!

blog.name: askdawnandvern
blog.title: Ask Dawn and Vern!
blog.description: Oh um, hello. I'm Dawn Bellwether. Yes, 'THAT' Dawn Bellwether. Ex-Assistant Mayor, Ex-Mayor, Ex-Criminal Mastermind, City Savior, Controversial Author and Predator/Prey Relationship Advocate. With the release of my book, "Predator seeking Prey", I've been getting a lot of public attention again. With that came a lot of questions. Vernon, my best friend and mate, thought it would be a good idea to deal with it directly by opening a blog and taking questions about our lives and our friends lives directly. So feel free to ask us questions...I guess?   (Blog Author Note: This blog is based on the story "The Rehabilitation of Dawn Bellwether" Which you can find on Fanfiction.net by yours truly WastedTimeEE. Aside from taking questions I am currently writing a sequel to the story which is in progress. This is my first time doing an ask blog and I hope you all like it. Oh, I'll also take questions too. Please donate to my Patreon.) Wasted Time's Patreon!
